{"tid":2250762,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"管浩鳴稱一切可以做的事情都已做 現在只有等台方通知","createTime":"2020-10-20T10:21:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T10:25:45.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2c47bea14bb237182cf05d5953101539b77ca07a","tid":2250762,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T10:21:44.000Z","msg":"管浩鳴稱一切可以做的事情都已做 現在只有等通知<br />\n<br />\n台灣殺人案死者潘曉穎的母親到政府總部外，讀出遞交予保安局局長李家超公開信的內容，包括對他未有回應訴求感到極度失望，亦提到希望疑犯陳同佳珍惜為他認罪求情的機會，盡快本星期五之前到台灣投案自首。<br />\n<br />\n協助陳同佳的聖公會教省秘書長管浩鳴，在與傳媒通訊平台中回應可否本周五前赴台及面對甚麼阻力等，他表示相信一切可以做的事情都已經做了，現在只有等通知，如果台灣律師有進一步消息，會再通知大家。<br />\n<br />\n他較早前證實，陳同佳至今未能取得入台簽證，又說當時接獲當局回覆是「暫時不能接受申請」，又指對方沒有要求申請人親臨櫃檯申請。<br />\n<br />\n管浩鳴上周被傳媒拍攝到帶同文件到位於金鐘、辦理港人赴台入境證的台北經濟文化辦事處。他其後回應查詢表示，正處理私人事情，不便透露情況。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1555748-20201020.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1555748-20201020.htm&d=h9s%2FmsO%2BhBO0acKdDJaYERYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=0f9d596a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1555748-20201020.htm&h=f29a151e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1555748-20201020.htm</a>"},{"pid":"85c2ce7d742e5c654fca3c0c49b031e7d18ca656","tid":2250762,"uid":278168,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T10:22:49.000Z","msg":"瀨浩鳴"},{"pid":"0313b22e3fae9ae2e888af7393352ed699781492","tid":2250762,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T10:23:18.000Z","msg":"放人未做"},{"pid":"73be67ecf0db937144bb09f9f021209cc17e97b5","tid":2250762,"uid":19196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T10:23:40.000Z","msg":"落地簽證啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b82141dcd7d7c04077dae5c52c0059fd8e10e6c1","tid":2250762,"uid":296677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T10:24:00.000Z","msg":"一班天真嬌<br />\n最開心係佳仔 唔洗去死"},{"pid":"3642508e00d9739bc3ad915eac3445d471ce1e31","tid":2250762,"uid":295452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T10:24:11.000Z","msg":"冇心情唔去"},{"pid":"be9d315ed9e350d6f74e8b531b845a8d0aafdc9d","tid":2250762,"uid":309553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T10:24:59.000Z","msg":"管浩嗚做了一切<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6ef87ac1004d90853c0aa693939c29db31f2f84","tid":2250762,"uid":10901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T10:25:45.000Z","msg":"想人同個自由人殺人犯一齊搭飛機咩"}]}